      <title>巴克莱计划在亚洲主要财富市场增加三倍员工</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/barclays-plans-hiring-spree-in-india-singapore-to-grow-wealth-management-teams</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴克莱银行亚洲地区财富业务主管表示，该银行计划在未来几年在亚洲大规模招聘，以扩大客户资产，重点关注印度和新加坡的超级富豪和家族办公室。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/barclays-plans-hiring-spree-in-india-singapore-to-grow-wealth-management-teams</guid>
